section.first
  .container.first__container
    a.first__link(href='#') New Book
    h1.first__title Mother Earth Hosts Our Travels
    p.first__descr There are not many cities that have experienced such social and political extremes in recent history as Amsterdam. In the 20th century alone, Amsterdam faced the atrocities of war for the first time in 400 years, became the radical center of 1960s social movements
    button.first__btn.btn-reset.btn Buy the Book
    .first__bottom
      form.first__form.search-form(action='#')
        input.search-form__field(type='search' placeholder='Search stories')
        button.search-form__button.btn-reset(type='submit' aria-label='Search stories')
      .first__slider.main-slider
        .swiper-container
          button.first__slider-btn.btn-left.btn-reset
          button.first__slider-btn.btn-right.btn-reset
          .swiper-wrapper
            .swiper-slide
              .main-slider__media
                button.main-slider__play.btn-reset
                video(src='/assets/videos/1.mp4' muted='' playsinline='')
              p.main-slider__text Wonderful Mountain
            .swiper-slide
              .main-slider__media
                img(src='/assets/img/slider-1.jpg' alt='Mountains')
              p.main-slider__text Wonderful Mountain
